mo&s;t able <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> their own Conceit) to advi&s;e others, can not write but thus &s;ini&s;terly, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> with their right hands. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">at pre&s;ent not <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ending to touch all the fond and un<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ound <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">pre&s;&s;ions, occuring almo&s;t in every Paragraph of the &s;aid Pamphlet, leaving it to &s;uch as by the <HI>poor dark Devil without a Body,</HI> page 1 &amp;c. are or may be concerned, to make their own Apology <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> &s;hall only take a little Notice,</P>
<P N="1">I Of &s;ome <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> words of the&s;e vain Braggard<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">.</P>
